comments: Johnson (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lee (GSW) and does not make contact during the screen.

Moody (GSW) is late to the spot and does not establish in a legal guarding position before the contact with Johnson (SAS). Replay review of the offensive foul called on Moody (GSW) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with Chiozza's (GSW) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) and Chiozza (GSW) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
White (SAS) makes marginal contact to Moody's (GSW) front as both players reach for the rebound.
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact to Moody's (GSW) front during his shot near the rim.
Chiozza (GSW) makes incidental contact with Murray's (SAS) arm after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Poole (GSW) slides his pivot foot after he gathers and before his shot attempt.
Kuminga (GSW) makes incidental contact with Murray (SAS) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Kuminga (GSW) and Murray (SAS) engage and disengage in the post.
Lee (GSW) and White (SAS) make marginal contact to each other's side as both pursue the missed shot.
During the loose ball, Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact to Moody's (GSW) body as he makes the pass.
Johnson (SAS) and Kuminga (GSW) engage and disengage after Johnson sets the pick.
Poole (GSW) legally contests Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) grabs and pulls Johnson's (SAS) jersey away from his body and affects his ability to rebound.
White (SAS) commits a take foul on Lee (GSW).
Bates-Diop (SAS) commits a take foul on Lee (GSW).
Poole (GSW) avoids making contact with Vassell (SAS) arm during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
